function myquantile(d::UnivariateDistribution, q::Number)
    θ = mean(d)
    tol = Inf
    while tol > 1e-5
        θold = θ
        θ = θ - (cdf(d, θ) - q) / pdf(d, θ)
        tol = abs(θold - θ)
    end
    θ
end
